     *  Occidental Chemical Corp. and Chemical Land Holdings Inc., both

     *  Occidental Chemical Corp. and Chemical Land Holdings Inc., both
Dallas-based firms, have agreed to spend at least $10 mil?lion for a
cleanup of dioxin contamination in Newark, N.J.  The state's Depart?ment of
Environmental Protection and the U.S. Environmental Protection Ag?ency
