Orlando, Fla.  An analysis of major environmental statutes.  The fee is
$895.  Sponsor:  GI, 301/251-9250.

     * Feb. 15-20, "American Association for the Advancement of Science
Annual Meeting," New Orleans.  Lectures, short courses and special sessions
on a variety of environmental issues.  The registration fee varies with
professional status and days attending.  Sponsor:  AAAS, Washington, D.C.,
202/326-6440.

     * Feb. 15-17, "Environmental Law," Washington, D.C.  Co-sponsored by
the Environmental Law Institute and the Smithsonian Institution.  The fee
is $450.  Contact:  American Bar Association, 800/253-6397 or 215/243-1630.



