order: All resulting contracts will contain a maximum ordermo). The Mo 
is a level that is established to assist customer agencies to determine 
when the break level for obtaining a price decrease has been reached. 
When an order exceeds this level, It is recommended that the agency 
seek aprice reduction, before placing the order. Option: All resulting 
contracts will include an option to extend the term of contract for an 
additional 5 yearperiod.  Advantage: All resulting contracts will 
require contractors to submit electronic contract data in a prescribed 
format for addition to GSA advantage, an on-line electronic database. 
