State activities outlined

     The Center for Economic Conversion released its
latest version of the "Economic Conversion Update."
     The report provides a comprehensive survey of
economic conversion activities in the states and details
what state and local governments and community
organizations are doing to help companies survive defense
downsizing. It also covers pending state legislation. The
price is $10. For more information call the Center for
Economic Conversion in Mountain View, Calif., at 415-
648-9186.





