<A NAME = "28"></A>Copyright
NAVY NEWS & UNDERSEA TECHNOLOGY via NewsNet
JANUARY 8, 1996

Bulk Liquid

     The Navy wants research in the area of bulk 
liquid transportation and dispensation under the 
"Maneuver From the Sea" doctrine. 
     Bulk liquids have to be provided to troops from 
the sea to scattered locations up to 100 miles inland. 
All material must be extremely ruggedized to 
withstand handling stress. 
     Respond by Jan. 31 to: Naval Facilities 
Command, Code 2711-5, Bldg. 41, 1000 23rd Ave., 
Port Hueneme, Calif. 93043-4301 (CBD, 12/19/95).




