JANUARY 8, 1996

E-2T Aircraft

     The Navy will contract with Hughes Aircraft 
Systems for technical support for the Ten One E air 
defense system associated with the E-2T early 
warning aircraft.
     For subcontracting opportunities contact Hughes' 
Ken Pardee at 714-732-9580 (CBD, 12/20/95).




